title: The Power Of Agreement | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Power Of Agreement | Joel Osteen
description:
Something powerful happens when you find someone to agree with God's promises over your life. If you'll get around people who will believe alongside you, you'll see God's favor released in a new way. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
